io.confluent.ksql.connect.supported

Interface SupportedConnector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Connectors, JdbcSource

    public interface SupportedConnector
    KSQL supports some "Blessed" connectors that we integrate well with. To be "blessed" means that we can automatically import topics created by these connectors and that we may provide templates that simplify configuration of these connectors.
